title: Default encryption method of B593s-931
answer:
B593s-931 support following encryption method 

 1.        SHARE authentication mode: WEP /NONE 

 2.        WPA-PSK authentication mode: AES/TKIP/TKIP+AES 

 3.        WPA2-PSK authentication mode: AES/TKIP/TKIP+AES 

 4.        WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK authentication mode: AES/TKIP/TKIP+AES 

 The default encryption method of B593s-931 is WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK authentication mode: TKIP+AES 

 If you changed encryption method of B593s-931 the Wi-Fi connection between PC and B593s-931 will be disconnected, please enter the new Wi-Fi key (Wi-Fi key of the encryption you selected) when you want to establish Wi-Fi connection.
